    <anchor n="T.50.2061.0801a16"/><head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date>京師安國寺<persName key="A010792">如淨</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0801a17"/><persName key="A010792">釋如淨</persName>，不詳何許人也。甫參法位，當納<lb
ed="T" n="0801a18"/>戒津，明練毘尼，砥礪名節。時恒講勗，徒侶<lb
ed="T" n="0801a19"/>雲屯。辭筆偕長，博達儒典。先是<placeName key="PL000000042002">關中</placeName>行<persName key="A001269">智<lb
ed="T" n="0801a20"/>首律師</persName>《四分律疏》，<placeName key="PL000000024082">魏郡</placeName><persName key="A000747">法礪律師</persName>著《疏》別行。<lb
ed="T" n="0801a21"/>爾時<placeName key="PL000000042002">關輔</placeName><placeName key="PL000000001520">河北</placeName>，各競宗派，微似參辰。<date from-iso="0609" key="j19435421973336" to-iso="0690">隋末唐<lb
ed="T" n="0801a22"/>初</date>，<persName key="A001519">道宣律師</persName>以首《大疏》為本，造《刪補律鈔》<lb
ed="T" n="0801a23"/>三卷，稍為會要，行事逗機。<date from-iso="0627" key="j19500921958296" to-iso="0649">貞觀</date>已來，<placeName key="PL000000042002">三輔</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000015039">江、<lb
ed="T" n="0801a24"/>淮</placeName>、<placeName key="PL000000035107">岷蜀</placeName>多傳唱之。次<persName key="A000294"><anchor xml:id="beg0801003"/>裝<anchor xml:id="end0801003"/></persName>三藏弟子<persName key="A001899">懷素</persName>者，<lb
ed="T" n="0801a25"/>先習《鈔宗》，後委棄<persName key="A001519">宣</persName>、<persName key="A000747">礪</persName>之學，於<date from-iso="0670" key="j19658611967498" to-iso="0674">咸亨年</date>中<lb
ed="T" n="0801a26"/>別述《開四分律記》，後號新章歟。至<date from-iso="0766" key="j20011912005747" to-iso="0779">代宗大<lb
ed="T" n="0801a27"/>曆</date>中，新章舊疏，互相長短。<date from-iso="0778-02-06" key="j20052552005608" to-iso="0779-01-25">十三年</date>，勅集三宗<lb
ed="T" n="0801a28"/>律匠，重定二家隆殺，時<persName key="A010792">淨</persName>推為宗主，語在<lb
ed="T" n="0801a29"/>《圓照傳》。至<date from-iso="0781-02-02" key="j20063472006701" to-iso="0782-01-22">建中二年</date>，奏二疏並行，<persName key="A010792">淨</persName>之力也。<pb ed="T" n="0801b" xml:id="T50.2061.0801b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0801b01"/>蓋以國相<persName key="A010790">元公載</persName>篤重素公，崇其律教，乃<lb
ed="T" n="0801b02"/>命<persName key="A010792">淨</persName>為新疏主作傳焉。</p>
